{"tid":2400953,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"19歲學生站近扔汽油彈人士被控暴動 警員疑中武漢肺炎未能出庭","createTime":"2021-02-09T10:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T11:54:53.000Z","uid":56115,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d01b04cec6e89931fd9a2033a5d5413e652957b6","tid":2400953,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T10:52:04.000Z","msg":"2019 年 8 月 31 日，本港多區發生衝突，警方晚上於銅鑼灣拘捕多人，控以暴動罪。其中一名被控暴動罪的 19 歲男學生，今（9 日）在區域法院受審。控方於開案陳詞指，暴動發生在晚上 8 時 10 分軒尼詩道近崇光百貨，有示威者向警方投擲汽油彈，被告與扔汽油彈的人站得非常靠近，並在逃跑時即場被制服。<br />\n<br />\n至於拘捕被告的警員昨日發高燒，正等待武漢肺炎檢測結果，今日未能出庭作供。<br />\n<br />\n控方指，案發時被告自願身處案發地點，知悉該處的情況，夥同其他參與暴動的身份不詳人士共同犯案，涉及最少 3 名或以上的人，於非法集結中干犯破壞社會安寧的行為，即向警務人員投擲汽油彈。"},{"pid":"03b9ffdbb524f5c7ba70df6a8643e3cdbdf1d50f","tid":2400953,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T10:52:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/831-%E9%8A%85%E9%91%BC%E7%81%A3%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-19-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E5%8F%97%E5%AF%A9-%E6%8E%A7%E6%96%B9%E6%8C%87%E7%AB%99%E8%BF%91%E6%89%94%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB-%E5%A4%A5%E5%90%8C%E7%8A%AF%E6%A1%88/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F831-%25E9%258A%2585%25E9%2591%25BC%25E7%2581%25A3%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-19-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25AF%25A9-%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%25AB%2599%25E8%25BF%2591%25E6%2589%2594%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB-%25E5%25A4%25A5%25E5%2590%258C%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A1%2588%2F&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMOL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=13e691ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F831-%25E9%258A%2585%25E9%2591%25BC%25E7%2581%25A3%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-19-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%25